{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/add-columns-with-grid-template-columns","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Dodaj red za `grid-template-columns`","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Samo kreiranje grid elementa nije dovoljno. Takođe morate definisati strukturu grida. Da biste dodali red u grid, koristite atribut <code>grid-template-columns</code> na grid elementu, kao što je prikazano ispod:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">.container {\r\n  display: grid;\r\n  grid-template-columns: 50px 50px;\r\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo će kreirati dva reda u vašoj mreži koje su svaki široki 50px. Broj parametara definisan za atribut <code>grid-template-columns</code> pokazuje broj redova u mreži, a vrednost svakog parametra pokazuje širinu svakog reda.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a9036d038fddaf9a66b5d32","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Tri reda u mrežnom kontejneru od kojih svaki je širine <code>100px</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/c7NzDHv","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301117,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/add-columns-with-grid-template-columns"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .d1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .d2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .d3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .d4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .d5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    \r\n  